{"tid":2123822,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"明串你呀熱狗！加州大學研究：拒絕戴口罩及不遵守社交距離者認知能力較低　","createTime":"2020-07-25T03:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T08:32:01.000Z","uid":10014,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"86c64b80e9a4f3d5b53046fdd43e02e62578d5de","tid":2123822,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:29:15.000Z","msg":"850人參與調查　證明拒絕戴口罩者認知能力低<br />\n<br />\n在街上見到有人拒絕戴口罩，以及不遵守社交距離，還與朋友聚會見面？最近加州大學心理學副教授張偉偉（Weiwei Zhang）和其研究團隊向850名美國市民進行調查，收集社交距離依從性、抑鬱情緒和焦慮感等數據，得出結論，拒絕戴口罩及不遵守社交距離的市民，其認知能力較其他人低。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gotrip.hk/569590/%e6%97%85%e9%81%8a/%e6%97%85%e9%81%8a%e7%86%b1%e8%a9%b1/%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e-%e4%b8%80%e6%88%b4%e4%b8%80%e9%9c%b2-%e8%aa%8d%e7%9f%a5%e8%83%bd%e5%8a%9b%e4%bd%8e/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gotrip.hk%2F569590%2F%25e6%2597%2585%25e9%2581%258a%2F%25e6%2597%2585%25e9%2581%258a%25e7%2586%25b1%25e8%25a9%25b1%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e-%25e4%25b8%2580%25e6%2588%25b4%25e4%25b8%2580%25e9%259c%25b2-%25e8%25aa%258d%25e7%259f%25a5%25e8%2583%25bd%25e5%258a%259b%25e4%25bd%258e%2F&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=6cb85835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gotrip.hk/569590/%e6%97%85%e9%81%8a/%e6%97%85%e9%81%8a%e7%86%b1%e8%a9%b1/%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e-%e4%b8%80%e6%88%b4%e4%b8%80%e9%9c%b2-%e8%aa%8d%e7%9f%a5%e8%83%bd%e5%8a%9b%e4%bd%8e/</a>"},{"pid":"d92047d5ba8144d0aa192c55abeed51d1c227dc9","tid":2123822,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:32:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5df761f1a7e7df5caa5edfb1a55e66d075898358","tid":2123822,"uid":10014,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wNArwrm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwNArwrm.jpg&h=11d1e033&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"